***************
Examples
***************
The following chapters include some of the example-procedures in /examples.
At the moment the creation of a procedure is fully text-based. Dont panic: it is easier than it looks like.
Go to :ref:`api`  to get all a full overview over the possibilities of ``diaGrabber``


